reviewText: Love these mysteries and Barnaby is always terrific!

All the episodes are very good: Dark Autumn, The Electric Vendetta and Who Killed Cock Robin.  Unfortunately, all three of these episodes are included in Set 3.  Usually Amazon lists the episode names in the description - however, none are listed in this case.  Very disappointing.
Can't wait to get the other sets.
Love the characters and the stories. I haven't seen any episodes without John Nettles in them though. Can't imagine the show without him and his TV family.
